#Fragment Britannia, Local, Britannia_Vesper {
  #Sophistication High {
    #Key "*museum*"{
      "On a lazy afternoon I like to wander around in Vesper's museum. It is the large building east of the tanner.",
      "The museum is a bit south of the customs house, and holds exquisite pieces of art and weaponry.",
      "South of the tavern is the city's museum. 'Tis an educational experience for the children, I think."
}
    #Key "*thiev*guild*"{
      "I'd hope we have no guild of thieves here!",
      "If I knew there was a thieves guild, I'd tell the guards first!",
      "I've heard rumors that thieves meet in the tanner's basement."
}
    #Key "*town hall*" "*city hall*"{
      "I hope thou hast had no trouble in Vesper, friend. The town hall is a southern island, one door south of the warriors' guild.",
      "I cannot guarantee that they can help thee there, but the town hall is one bridge away from the southern inn.",
      "Look thou to the southern side of Vesper... where the Soldiers' Guild is ... for the town hall."
}
    #Key "*alchemist*" {
      "Indeed, we have an alchemist  ... a very busy one, at that! Thou'lt find the shop to the very north of town.",
      "If thou'rt looking for potions, the shop thou needest is to the far north of Vesper, on the same island as the Jeweler.",
      "Look thou to the northern isle ... where the Bardic Guild is ... for the alchemist's shop."
}
    #Key "*tailor*" {
      "The tailor is on the eastern shore of the river. Take the bridge from the northern isle and then go south.",
      "We've a fine tailor, if a little difficult to get to. Make thy way to the east shore. The tailor and the bank are neighbors.",
      "The tailor is neighbor to the Sorcerer's Guild ... if thou dost not mind a watery path!"
}
    #Key "*provisioner*" "*supplies*" {
      "Thou'lt be wanting supplies, I take it? The provisioner keeps a shop to the north of town, on the shore.",
      "Our provisioner makes a brisk trade, with all the importing and exporting this city sees. His shop is just off the northern island where the Jeweler is found.",
      "Thou canst buy supplies at the Provisioner's shop, on the shore close by the northern island."
      "Supplies can be had at the provisioner's shop. If thou'rt lucky, they'll be a new shipment in from the docks.",
      "The provisioner can sell thee just about anything thou couldst need. Look to the largest island on the south side of Vesper to find the shop.",
      "Provisions can be had for a price. Just bring thy coin to the shop on the north side of the largest southern island."
}
    #Key "*bank*" {
      "Our bank is on the northmost island. Look for the jeweler and the painter's studio.",
      "Thou'rt wanting a bank? A withdrawal or a deposit, I wonder .... Thou'lt need to head to the northern isle of Vesper. It is somewhat to the north, where the river branches.",
      "Thou'rt looking for the bank? Look to the north, where the river first branches. The bank is the largest building on that isle."
}
    #Key "*mage*" {
      "There are mages who will sell their talents, true enough. Merely look on the ground floor of their guildhall on the north island.",
      "The sorcerers get together in their guild hall on the north island. Those who wish to earn some coin can be found on the ground floor!",
      "Magic users aren't allergic to gold, and that's a fact. Look on the ground floor of that hall they've got on the northern island, and thou'lt find a mage who will do as thee bid."
}
    #Key "*alchemist*" {
      "Indeed, we have an alchemist ... a very busy one, at that! Thou'lt find the shop to the very north of town.",
