      "Look thou to the northern isle ... where the Bardic Guild is ... for the alchemist's shop."
}
    #Key "*sorcer*guild*" "*magic*guild*" "*magic*hall*" {
      "There are a fair number of sorcerers here, and that's a fact. They meet in the upper floors of their hall on the north island.",
      "The sorcerers get together in their guild hall on the north island. Sometimes, when they use too much power, all the candles on the island will puff out, and it will be hours before they light again!",
      "Magic users don't like each other, by and large, but they'll meet in that hall they've got on the northern island, just so they can waggle their eyebrows at each other!"
}
    #Key "*jewel*" {
      "The jeweler keeps shop on the northern island, betwixt the miners' and bards' guild halls.",
      "Gems can be had from the Jeweler's shop on the northernmost island.",
      "If thou hast an eye for things that sparkle, get thee to the Jewelers store, just north of the Bardic Guild."
}
    #Key "*paint*" "*art*" {
      "If it's art that thou'rt interested in ... there's an artist's place on the northernmost isle.",
      "I'll tell thee for free ... there's a fine artist on the northern isle that's none too busy to be useful.",
      "The best artist's studio, and by coincidence the only one, is on the northern isle, near the guild houses."
}
    #Key "*beekeep*" {
      "Thou canst understand why the beekeeper is on a little island all alone! 'Tis a little piece of land in the northernmost part of Vesper, across the bridge from either the painter's studio, or the bakery.",
      "The bee hives are kept on a small islet at the northeast. 'Tis north of the butcher and baker, and east of the painter's studio.",
