      "The miners meet in their hall on the northernmost island. The building is on the southern end if that isle.",
      "The miners, they don't have a lot to complain about, I don't think. Mining is a good way of fillin' a purse. Still ... they built themselves a meetin' place on the northern island, just so's they can talk."
}
    #Key "*bard*guild*" {
      "The Bardic Guild is on the northernmost island.",
      "Lookin' for the Bards' Guild? 'Tis the southernmost building on the northernmost island of Vesper.",
      "Is it bards thou'rt lookin' for? Head to the northern island and follow the music.",
      "The Bards' Guild is the first building thou'lt come across, after taking the bridge north from the Tinker's place."
