    #Key "*bakery*" {
      "The baker's place is on the island just north of the docks.",
      "If thou knows where the beekeeper is, just take the bridge south from there to find the baker's island.",
      "Good bread is fit for any man, king or beggar, I say. Our baker keeps shop on one of the eastern islands ... the one just north of the docks."
