    #Key "*butcher*" "*meat*"{
      "Thou'rt looking for the butcher, I take it. Get thee to the docks, then take the bridge north from that island. The butcher is the first building thou'lt see.",
      "The butcher can be found on that northeast island, clustered with the baker, farmer and fisher's shops.",
      "If thou hast found the beekeeper's island, take the southern bridge from there and thou'lt be within sight of the butcher."
}
    #Key "*produce*" "*farm*" {
      "The farmer brings his produce in from the fields and sells it from his shop on the island just north of the docks.",
      "The produce stall is nearest the baker and fisher ... just south of the beekeeper's island.",
      "If thou takest the bridge north of the Seaman's Guild - near to the docks, thou knowest - the farmer's shop is north and east on the small island thou'lt find."

}
    #Key "*fish*" {
      "There is naught but fresh fish in Vesper, and 'tis easiest had from the fisherman's shop. Look near the baker and butcher's places.",
      "There be no old fish when the fisher's shop is right on the water, I'll warrant. Take the north bridge from the docks, then head east for the best fish in Vesper.",
      "The fish shop is on an island in the northeast section of Vesper. All the food shops are. The island is south of the bees and north of the quays."
