    #Key "*armour*" "*armor*" {
      "If thou'rt in need of armour, look on the central westernmost island of Vesper.",
      "The armourer is beside the southernmost bardic guild.",
      "The best armour can be bought on a small island, one bridge north of the blacksmith, one bridge west of the Tinker."
}
    #Key "*bowyer*" {
      "I think we have a bowyer. I've never been there myself.",
