      "The woodworker is just west of the Seaman's Guild, but it takes a fair bit of walking on bridges to get there."
}
    #Key "*sea*guild*" {
      "I still do not think 'tis a proper thing to have the Seaman's Guild on dry land, but I suppose an island is better than mainland. Look near the docks to find it.",
